#adidasSkateboarding #IWD #InternationalWomensDay 
🎥 @torstenfrank @samuelmcguire

Busenitz Indoor Super XV /// Celebrating 15-years with Dennis Busenitz. Guided by Busenitz’s creative vision and insights, the Busenitz Indoor Super takes cues from the past and introduces them to the present. The iconic Busenitz upper is merged with a vintage outsole inherited from an adidas indoor model from the 80s. The XV across the heels commemorates the 15-year anniversary of adidas x Busenitz. Available in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding
•
#adidasSkateboarding #DennisBusenitz
